Auto tune kiln then save PID settings to corrosponding kiln config number
To use ,copy to main Nemesis PI directory delete current config then rename your config kiln 4 for example  to "config.py"
then start controller as normal in manual mode or if you wish to stick to the same kiln set up auto boot function see manual
that comes with your nemesis pi

Once config has been copied you need to when using manual mode restart TERMINAL then open up controller program again
If Using Auto Booting You Must Restart the Nemess PI Rogue 
After following above steps New PID settings will be applied

Several Kiln Configs can be found on your Nemesis PI Rogue in file explorer /home/pi/NemesisPI/storage